# Config file for weather module
# Here we define the list of weather replacement effects
# used for evaporating puddles from a map.
#
# File format is as follows:
# - name of arch or object to find
# - name of arch to place over the found tile
#   Can be NONE to denote when the object is removed.
# - name of arch to place atop both,
#   or NONE if there is not a second object to place
#   for this substitution. For evaporation, this
#   is likely NONE.
# - 1 if the first field refers to an archetype name,
#   0 if that field refers to an object name.
#   Current handling of this in the code assumes evaporation
#   is always set to handle the archetype name.

rain1_weather, NONE, NONE, 1
rain2_weather, rain1_weather, NONE, 1
rain3_weather, rain2_weather, NONE, 1
rain4_weather, rain3_weather, NONE, 1
rain5_weather, rain4_weather, NONE, 1
mountain1_rivlets_weather, NONE, NONE, 1
mountain2_rivlets_weather, NONE, NONE, 1
